- Update to version 1.6.0
  + Bug fixes
    - Multiple dialogs (e. g. Settings dialog) could be shown at
      the same time
    - Resources could freeze sometimes after the device wakes up
      from sleep
    - Apps installed in local folders (e. g. /usr/local/share) were
      not recognized
